{"id":"5850","name":"bright-early-feeling-viral-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Feeling Viral Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2010-10-11T10:45:00-05:00","tags":["anaheim ducks","apartment fires","dallas cowboys","donald wood","drought","flood buyouts","gas prices","georgia","mcgavock high school","nashville flood","nashville predators","preds","second harvest food bank","tent city","titans","viral video","world zombie day","youtube","zombie walk"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/39296163@N08/5066380188/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4111/5066380188_0f63726291.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"278\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Good morning, Nashville. Last Friday, <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13294468\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">McGavock High School math teacher Donald Wood had a meltdown during class in which he threw some tables, screamed a lot and admitted to starting a fire in the school bathroom one time</a>. Wood was subdued and carted off in an ambulance, but not before one enterprising student caught the whole incident on cell phone video and put it on Youtube. As of this morning, <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13300210\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">the video has almost 136,000 views and school officials are trying to find a way to &#x201C;remove it from the Internet,&#x201D;</a> except that&#x2019;s just not how the internet works, you see. They&#x2019;re also looking into disciplining the student since he wasn&#x2019;t supposed to have his cell phone out in class. You can watch it&#xA0;<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9RLp8wZAlE\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.youtube.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p><ul><li><strong>Where there&#x2019;s smoke.</strong> We never thought we&#x2019;d be saying this after May&#x2019;s deluge, but Tennessee is experiencing a drought. As such,<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20101011/NEWS01/10110318/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"> you should be very careful if you&#x2019;re planning to burn anything outside because we&#x2019;ve had a bit of a fire problem lately</a> (like <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/25350595/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">this one in West Nashville that burned for three days</a>) with everything being dry and hot. This is actually the biggest drought we&#x2019;ve had since the 2007/2008 water shortage which <a href=\"http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,330113,00.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.foxnews.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">led Georgia to try to hack off part of our state and steal our water</a>.</li><li><strong>Help fire victims. </strong>Speaking of fires, lots of you have been asking about how to assist victims of the apartment fires in the past few weeks. <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/how-help-fire-victims?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+NashvilleCityPaper-CityNews+(Nashville+City+Paper+-+City+News)&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Read about all the ways you can help them out</a>.</li><li><strong>Win and win</strong>. It was a great weekend for sports in Nashville with <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/sports/goals-come-goalie-goes-predators-season-opening-victory?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+NashvilleCityPaper-Sports+(Nashville+City+Paper+-+Sports)&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">the Preds raking in four goals to topple the Anaheim Ducks (and win everyone free Frosties!)</a> in their home opener, and <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/Global/story.asp?S=13300004\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">the Titans taking down the Cowboys</a>.</li><li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces.</strong> About <a href=\"http://www.fox17.com/template/inews_wire/wires.regional.tn/2c1513c2-www.fox17.com.shtml\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.fox17.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">82% of the folks who are eligible for flood buyouts so far have been taking them</a> &#x2026; Nashville celebrated World Zombie Day on Saturday <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13299404\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">with a charitable twist</a> &#x2026; City Paper brings us <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/creating-new-place-nashvilles-homeless?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+NashvilleCityPaper-LatestNews+(Nashville+City+Paper+-+Latest+News)&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">the latest on Tent City</a> &#x2026; Brace yourselves for <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20101011/NEWS01/101011020/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">gas prices on the rise</a> &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20101011/NEWS01/101011012/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Cooler weather and some much-needed rai</a>n could be in the cards for us this week.</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/39296163@N08/5066380188/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>hikeandhistory</em></a><em>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/10/15/bright-early-well-take-the-boat-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: We&#x2019;ll Take The Boat Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: We&#x2019;ll Take The Boat Edition</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/04/30/bright-not-so-early-feeling-texty-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; (Not So) Early: Feeling Texty Edition\">Bright &amp; (Not So) Early: Feeling Texty Edition</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}